node.text: Here’s a SNEAK-PEEK of #HalloweenWars premiering on @Foodnetwork September 19th! #Ghosttober

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zak Bagans in Helper, Utah with @aarongoodwin. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Ive been through a lot of scary doorways but this one to the underground in “Carbon County Chaos” messed a lot of us up. Stream now on #discoveryplus NEW Ghost Adventures

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zak Bagans in 𝓊𝓃𝓀𝓃𝑜𝓌𝓃. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Your moments of the past may confuse your present self but deep inside you know theres another you from a time beyond.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zak Bagans in Food Network Studios. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: Announcement: Hey everyone, I am so excited to announce that I have joined the new season of “Halloween Wars”, premiering Sunday September 19th at 9pm ET/PT on @foodnetwork and discovery+. During the entire season I take inspiration from my collection of haunted & mysterious artifacts from my Haunted Museum in Las Vegas to challenge the teams to create frighteningly intricate cakes that are as spooky as they are tasty! Get ready!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zak Bagans in Hollywood Toys and Costumes. May be an image of text that says 'discovery+ NEW Y GHOST ADVENTURES THURSDAY 29TH JULY'.

node.text:
Get ready tomorrow for one of creepiest & most POLTERGEIST active buildings Ive stepped foot inside...

“Terror at the Toy Shop” NEW #GhostAdventures streams tomorrow on @discoveryplus

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zak Bagans in Ghost Adventures. May be an image of 4 people and text that says 'GHOST ADVENTURES New Season Streaming Now discovery+'.

node.text: NEW SEASON of Ghost Adventures is NOW streaming on #DiscoveryPlus kickin off with “The Great Saltair Curse”
